Orbit AI Essay Editor Project  
This project is a web-based essay editor enhanced with AI features. It allows users to write essays, analyze clarity, readability, and tone, rephrase text, fix grammar, summarize content, and apply tone transformations using AI. The backend is built with Node.js, and the frontend uses React with React Quill and Vite.

